column5: Just returned from the Raptors game that i went to with tickets from the Fishign for Tyler auction.   Not sure who donated them, but i wanted to say thank you.  They were phenomenal seats.  Really, really fantastic.  Great game as well.
and a rare victory. After the dino-egg they laid in NYC I'm shocked they won
Glad you had a good time....  Maureen
Glad you enjoyed it  Donated by: Franklin Empire Inc ( Lighting and electrical wholesaler)  TB
Thank you Franklin Empire Inc......great seats.  Much appreciated.
